Daniel Stenberg (23 Feb 2016)
- web: the site is now HTTPS

- RELEASE-NOTES: 1.7.0 release

- diffie_hellman_sha256: convert bytes to bits
  
  As otherwise we get far too small numbers.
  
  Reported-by: Andreas Schneider
  
  CVE-2016-0787

